data.title: Opened a bad PDF two weeks ago.
data.meta_description: I accidentally opened a malicious PDF from a trusted contact a few weeks ago. My disk is running at 50% constantly while connected to the internet, my video driver crashes constantly in ARK:Survival, I found out last night SFC /Scannow will not complete even in safemode and Powershell.exe crashes...
